OL,6,FIsland Energy has announced that
OL,7,Fpeople in who experienced disruption
OL,8,Fto their gas supply in October last
OL,9,Fyear will be receiving a refund as a
OL,10,F"gesture of goodwill".
OL,12,FIt comes after thousands of for weeks
OL,13,Ffollowing an island-wide fault on
OL,14,FSaturday 7 October 2023.
OL,16,FA payment of #11.56 will be made in
OL,17,Fthe form of a credit to each
OL,18,Fcustomer's account and will be applied
OL,19,Fin February 2024.
