OL,6,FShe added: "As gas systems are
OL,7,Frelatively complex, they cannot be
OL,8,Fimmediately reinstated, and proper
OL,9,Fprocesses must be followed to
OL,10,Freintroduce supply.
OL,12,F"As a result of this supply outage,
OL,13,FIsland Energy will be refunding the
OL,14,Fstanding charge for October to
OL,15,Fcustomers as a gesture of goodwill."
OL,17,FBusiness and commercial customers have
OL,18,Fbeen reviewed by Island Energy on a
OL,19,Fcase-by-case basis.
