OL,6,FIsland Energy say whilst all customers
OL,7,Fwill receive the credit on their
OL,8,Faccount, most businesses have
OL,9,Finsurance for this type of disruption
OL,10,Fand it has been proven that this is
OL,11,Ftypically the best route to recover
OL,12,Fwhat was lost.
OL,14,FChief Executive of Island Energy
OL,15,Fadded: "As there is no requirement for
OL,16,Fenergy companies in Jersey to have pre-
OL,17,Fagreed compensation schemes in place
OL,18,Fwe have been working with our
OL,19,Finsurance company to ascertain whether
OL,20,Fwe were covered for this event.
