OL,6,F"Unfortunately, as it was a total loss
OL,7,Fof supply due to circumstances out of
OL,8,Four control, the insurance company has
OL,9,Fconfirmed that it will not be covered.
OL,11,F"We recognise that this is
OL,12,Fdisappointing for our customers and
OL,13,Fare therefore committed to refunding
OL,14,Fthe entire month of October, rather
OL,15,Fthan just the period of the outage."
